summary:
A results driven individual with strong entrepreneurial spirit and a proven track record of business development, product management, team coordination, digital merchandising and online content production who drives for excellence. 

I have been working in digital media for some of the world's most attractive brands such as Disney, Expedia, MTV and BBC Worldwide. 

At the moment I'm also doing a Master degree in 'Digital Media Management'​ at Hyper Island.

https://about.me/juanmunozcaicoya
